              <li style="color:black;">3. At the end, copy the embed code and paste in the article body</li>
          </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="browseLinkedVideoModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="browseLinkedVideoModal" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title" style="color:black;" id="exampleModalLongTitle">Browse Linked Videos</h5>
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
          <ul>
              <li style="color:black;">1. Click <a href="https://www.rumble.com/upload.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a></li>
              <li style="color:black;">2. Follow their upload instructions</li>
              <li style="color:black;">3. At the end, copy the embed code and paste in the article body</li>
